                  </span>
                </td>
              </tr>
              <tr>
                <td>
                  <a name="x-http://314e.com/fhir/CodeSystem/attachment-tag-hidden"> </a>
                  <code>http://314e.com/fhir/CodeSystem/attachment-tag</code>
                </td>
                <td style="white-space:nowrap">  
                  <a href="CodeSystem-attachment-tag.html#attachment-tag-hidden">hidden</a>
                </td>
                <td>Hidden from application use</td>
                <td>
                  <div>
                    <p>Indicates to the consumer application that this attachment should
not be used even though it exists in the data.</p>

                    <p>This may be used to identify the preferred/usable attachment when
multiple copies of equivalent content are available.</p>

                  </div>
